Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.210 --> 00:00:04.280
The solution has a few steps. First, the texture's loaded. Then, it's wrap mode

00:00:04.280 --> 00:00:08.860
is set to repeat. And the repeat factor itself is set to 10 for each axis. The

00:00:08.860 --> 00:00:13.280
materials map is then set to the texture to display the grass. Feel free to

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:16.680
remove the grid lines, of course. If you do, you'll see that the bird doesn't

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.710
feel very attached to the surface, since there's no shadow.

